# Container

The goal of this view is to wrap your sections and either centers it or make it full width depending on the selected container `type`.

## Features

{% for spec in props(specs.props) %}
- `{{ spec }}`
{% endfor %}

## Usage

#### Blade

```php
@include('sugar.bare.container.container', [
    'type' => [
        'default' => '',
        'wide' => 'full'
    ],
    'content' => '
        <h2>Hello world</h2>
    ',
    'margin' => [
        'default' => [
            'bottom' => '50'
        ],
        'mobile' => [
            'bottom' => '20'
        ]
    ]
])
```

#### Twig

```twig
{{ '{%' }} include 'sugar.bare.container.container' with {
    type: {
        default: '',
        wide: 'full'
    },
    content: '<h2>Hello world</h2>',
    margin: {
        default: {
            bottom: '50'
        },
        mobile: {
            bottom: '20'
        }
    }
} {{ '%}' }}
```

